    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>:</p><p>If this Skill is a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Charged Attack</span>: Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Conductive </span>to the opponent's active character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Conductive</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>This status starts with 2 stacks of Conductive. When attached repeatedly, Conductive stack +1. Conductive can be stacked to a maximum of 4 stacks.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Accumulate 1 stack of Conductive.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character attached with Conductive takes DMG from Violet Arc: </span>Remove this status and DMG +1 for each stack of Conductive.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/ead1e5139681f49400a80a2ebb10fb2a_3123825160474304392.png",
                "id": "talent35813",
                "key": "Lightning Touch",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lightning Touch"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p>If Conductive is not attached to the opponent's active character, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Conductive </span>will be attached.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Conductive</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p>This status starts with 2 stacks of Conductive. When attached repeatedly, Conductive stack +1. Conductive can be stacked to a maximum of 4 stacks.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Accumulate 1 stack of Conductive.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character attached with Conductive takes DMG from Violet Arc: </span>Remove this status and DMG +1 for each stack of Conductive.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/af99fb6b223af8aab53e4447b06483ba_8718823516849760484.png",
                "id": "talent72130",
                "key": "Violet Arc",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Violet Arc"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>. Summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lightning Rose</span>. The opponent's active character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Conductive</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/e225f8fa5e9a435290d33b7b93b4e376_1223538925514398807.png",
                "id": "talent4470",
                "key": "Lightning Rose",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lightning Rose"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/1a3db5c5531fb4444758f49100411b27_4695937740805367061.png",
                "id": "talent40924",
                "key": "Lightning Rose",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/27/35428890/2b3f9718f47e31a775816000450f000e_6916830800288857251.png",
                "title": "Lightning Rose"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/590b25464c1f468fde608bd9c7f06fb0_4612111449477369568.png",
                "id": "talent71077",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Before your Action Phase, should the total number of your Elemental Dice be even, your Normal Attack will be considered a Charged Attack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/14/35428890/1fafbff4b60b57a39c1f9a8c226a3a6b_82032909243019551.png",
